Mean Servers Limited specializes in Cloud Hosting, Virtual Private Servers, Dedicated Servers, and Server Management. Mean Servers focuses on quality, not quantity. Some providers promise you the world and you get nothing in the end, we promise you exactly what is stated here and nothing less!

*Windows and DirectAdmin are included free on plans that have the minimum resources required to run them properly*

Our network is superior. All of our nodes are on a 1Gbps port, take a look with our &lt;a href="https://www.meanservers.com/looking-glass.php"&gt;looking glass just to see how amazing our network is&lt;/a&gt;. We also are dual stacked supporting both IPv4 and IPv6 natively, no tunnels here!

Every Linux 512MB and 1GB LET Special VPS Plan we sell includes a free DirectAdmin license for the life of the service you have with Mean Servers along with the initial install for FREE. All of our servers boast the newest generation of components made by leading brands such as Dell and HP. Mean Servers NEVER oversells and keeps a cloud platform making it easy to move your VPS to a new node if you wish to upgrade your plan. Every VPS plan also includes access to our Virtualizor VPS Control Panel allowing our clients to reboot, shutdown, VNC, change root passwords, and reload the operating system without intervention from us. All of our VPS plans utilize KVM technology giving you privacy, speed, guaranteed resources, and root access.

Mean Servers also has 24/7 support available via live chat, ticket system, and coming in the next month, phone support. All of our support technicians are 100% USA based and in house, we do not outsource our support team and never will!

